CADI.Common.Cache

Class DataBin

  • java.lang.Object
    • CADI.Common.Cache.DataBin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClassIdentifiers
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MainHeaderDataBin, MetaDataBin, PrecinctDataBin, TileHeaderDataBin

    public class DataBin
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassIdentifiers
    This class is a container for JPEG2000 Data-bins. Data-bins contain portions of a JPEG2000 file or codestream data, which can be based of precincts, tiles, headers, or metadata.

    Further information, see ISO/IEC 15444-9 section A.3

    Version:
    1.1.2 2011/09/06
    Author:
    Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)
